{
  "stem": "20745.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were worried about me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't see me on the-- on the-- with the people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then I came home, and I-- they were afraid they gonna look for me-- they'll come to look for me because I was there, and I disappeared.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they send me to this man again from the mill, and I was there-- I was hiding there for a few days in the attic.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they didn't come to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I went home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the house.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, with my brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the-- the older than me, not the oldest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The oldest had a-- a-- he had a passport-- an Irish passport, and he went to [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Warsaw. ?] And he-- like a Polack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they-- oh, they were-- they killed them two, because he-- he wasn't-- they were in a different farm, and they didn't work because they were too young yet.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they slept in a-- also in an attic by a Gentile.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one Gentile told the Germans that two Jews are sleeping there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took them out and killed them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were dead already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You could imagine, but it was-- they were very bad, very bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they used to come in town and take out the Jews and put them in the mart and beat them, but not-- until then, not so many.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only even the, you know, the Poles used to say-- they didn't know who was Jewish or not.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans didn't know, but the Poles helped them a lot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My baby sister-- they had to take-- they gave orders right in the beginning that they should take out the-- the small children to a town Parczew-- P-A-R-C-Z-E-W.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
